(:summary    "Control rtorrent from GNU Emacs"
 :created    "2010"
 :updated    "2011"
 :license    "GPL-3"
 :authors    (("Stefan Kangas" . "skangas@skangas.se"))
 :maintainer ("Stefan Kangas" . "skangas@skangas.se")
 :provided   (mentor url-scgi)
 :required   ((("cl" cl)
	       ("xml-rpc" xml-rpc)))
 :keywords   (bittorrent rtorrent)
 :homepage   "https://github.com/skangas/mentor"
 :commentary "\
This is a GNU Emacs interface for the `rtorrent' bittorrent client.  It uses
XML-RPC to communicate with rtorrent, and needs rtorrent to be configured
accordingly.  This project aims to provide a feature complete interface.

TODO:
Filters
Sort according to column, changable with < and >
Customizable fonts
Save cache to disk

Bug reports, comments, and suggestions are welcome!")
